data.description: GORGEOUS MUST SEE 3/2 with bonus room in quiet SE Palm Bay! Home has been completely remodeled - move in ready! New ceramic tile and laminate flooring. New fans and fixtures throughout! Kitchen features stainless appliances, new granite countertops, new cabinets, and large pantry! Spacious master suite with lots of closet space! Master bath features large walk-in shower, dual sinks, his/her closets, and large tub! Large bonus room can be office, nursery, playroom - the possibilities are endless! Huge porch has been completely enclosed with windows and AC unit - perfect for entertaining and enjoying the backyard! Roof and exterior paint 2019, water heater 2021, AC condenser 2023 . WILL NOT LAST!
